head.note:
In English and Amharic;
                                    Amharic text not printed. Ratification advised by the Senate,
                                    Sept. 15, 1914; ratified by the President, Sept. 19, 1914;
                                    Prince Lidj Yassou notified of ratification, Dec. 20, 1914;
                                    proclaimed, Aug. 9, 1920.
